prompts.frontCover:
A humorous and lighthearted watercolor illustration for a birthday card front. The scene features two people, Lao Lao and Jordan, transformed into cartoon/illustrated characters that highly resemble their appearance in the reference photos, including their exact clothing (without text/logos), hairstyles, facial features, and body proportions.

Lao Lao is joyfully holding a large, steaming dim sum basket overflowing with cartoonish, smiling shumai and har gow. Jordan is standing next to her, playfully trying to sneak a dumpling from the basket with a pair of oversized chopsticks, a mischievous grin on their face. They are both looking at each other with warm, laughing expressions. The background is a soft, abstract wash of pastel colors, suggesting a cheerful atmosphere without specific details.

The entire illustration is rendered in a beautiful, flat 2D watercolor style with soft, flowing colors, visible artistic brush strokes, a subtle paper texture, and organic paint bleeds at the edges.

Centered in the middle of the card, in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script, is the text: "Happy Birthday, Lao Lao!"

- Reference photos provided for character creation
- Characters should only appear on the front cover
- Transform real people into artistic cartoon/illustrated versions matching the style
- Maintain recognizable features while adapting to the artistic style
